title: Gunman in the Streets (1950 Film Noir) starring Dane Clark | Director Frank Tuttle

sources.title: Gunman in the Streets (1950 Film Noir) starring Dane Clark | Director Frank Tuttle
sources.description:
Eddie Roback an escaped gangster struggling to flee Paris as the police dragnet closes around him, with his former lover Denise caught in the crossfire.

Original title: Gunman in the Streets (1950)
Alternative Titles: Gangster at Bay, O Criminoso não Dorme, Le traqué, Traqué, El tiempo se agota, Sie war ihm hörig, Unterwelt von Paris

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/a9wJl-e_8Bk


Director: Frank Tuttle
Writers: Jacques Companéez, Maximilien Ilyin, Henry Kane
Starring: Simone Signoret, Dane Clark, Fernand Gravey
Genres: Classics, Crime, Drama, Film-Noir
Release Date: December 13, 1950 (Paris)
